@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<main class="main">
    <div class="page-title">
        <div class="container d-lg-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
            <h1 class="mb-2 mb-lg-0">Privacy Policy</h1>
        </div>
    </div>

    <section class="section py-5">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 840px;">
            <p class="text-muted small mb-4">Last updated: March 28, 2026</p>

            <p>
                Qaro2a (“we,” “our,” or “us”) operates this website and related services. This Privacy Policy explains how we
                collect, use, disclose, and safeguard information when you visit our store, create an account, or place an
                order.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Information we collect</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Account and profile data:</strong> name, email address, and password (stored securely) when you register.</li>
                <li><strong>Order and Delivery data:</strong> items purchased, exact delivery address, and a reachable phone number. Since we operate on a <strong>Cash on Delivery (COD)</strong> basis, we do not collect or store credit card or bank account information.</li>
                <li><strong>Content Submissions:</strong> book titles, descriptions, manuscripts, and author profiles you upload to our platform.</li>
                <li><strong>Technical data:</strong> IP address, browser type, device information, and cookies or similar technologies as described below.</li>
                <li><strong>Communications:</strong> messages you send us through contact forms or support channels.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">How we use your information</h2>
            <p>We use the information to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>process and fulfill orders, and coordinate delivery via your provided phone number;</li>
                <li>manage your account and authenticate you;</li>
                <li>improve our website, products, and services;</li>
                <li>send transactional or service-related messages (e.g., order confirmations);</li>
                <li>comply with legal obligations and protect our rights and users.</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Cookies and similar technologies</h2>
            <p>
                We use cookies and similar technologies for essential site functionality, preferences, and
                security. You can control cookies through your browser settings; disabling some cookies may limit certain
                features.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Sharing of information</h2>
            <p>
                We share your name, address, and phone number with <strong>shipping and delivery partners</strong> solely to deliver your orders. 
                We do not share payment data with online gateways as we use Cash on Delivery. We may disclose information if required by law or to protect
                the safety, rights, or property of Qaro2a, our users, or others.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Data retention</h2>
            <p>
                We retain information for as long as needed to provide our services, meet legal and accounting requirements,
                and resolve disputes.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Your choices and rights</h2>
            <p>
                Depending on where you live, you may have rights to access, correct, delete, or restrict processing of your
                personal information. To exercise these rights, contact us using the details below.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Security</h2>
            <p>
                We implement reasonable technical and organizational measures to protect your information. No method of
                transmission or storage is completely secure; we cannot guarantee absolute security.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Children’s privacy</h2>
            <p>
                Our services are not directed to children under the age where parental consent is required.
                We do not knowingly collect personal information from children in violation of applicable law.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Changes to this policy</h2>
            <p>
                We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated
                policy where permitted by law.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h4 mt-4">Contact us</h2>
            <p>
                For privacy-related questions, contact us at
                <a href="mailto:qaro2a.official@gmail.com">qaro2a.official@gmail.com</a>.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>